{"tid":1481104,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球最少33個城市有集會聲援香港示威者","createTime":"2019-08-17T14:46:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T15:13:17.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d37e0ad6d74e191d947378f8011608eddfe60d","tid":1481104,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"全球最少33個城市周末都有民眾集會，聲援香港的反修例示威者。在倫敦，大批民眾在特拉法加廣場集會，部分人遊行到唐寧街首相府和國會大樓，促請英國政府支持港人訴求和履行對香港的道義責任。<br />\n<br />\n而在澳洲墨爾本，約2000人周五晚在州立圖書館外集會，批評香港警方濫用武力。期間有手持五星旗的民眾到場指罵集會人士，引發衝突。墨爾本警方說，尊重社會人士和平及合法表達意見，但強調不會縱容違法、暴力或反社會行為。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的蔡英文總統強調，全球多個國家對香港局勢表達關切，期望香港的自由民主得到落實。台灣的安全部門持續監看香港情況，準備因應的措施。"},{"pid":"a6d7b233b554a8bba25cf28ccb428b53a73123f3","tid":1481104,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"[美國旗]Reddit: Be the America Hong Kong thinks we are.<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481034</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7696e4c652d88b22843ecad0b02eb21bfa8339da","tid":1481104,"uid":271539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:59:21.000Z","msg":"英國<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xo52j9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXo52j9a.jpg&h=ccf59fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cBwXVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cBwXVU.jpg&h=8c3c0eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dh0BpAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDh0BpAX.jpg&h=7a352984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVJSHnF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVJSHnF.jpg&h=159333f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aabbcbfb13aaaa785aab2d23c397947cc437bb05","tid":1481104,"uid":108337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"攬炒團隊幫助左好多<br />\n仲有世界各地既香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}